                                  <source media="(min-width:576px)" srcset="~/Content/img/SumoSpin/timelinesmall.jpg">
                                  <source media="(min-width:250px)" srcset="~/Content/img/SumoSpin/timelinesmall.jpg"
                                          sizes="(max-width: 450px)">
                                  <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/img/SumoSpin/timelinesmall.jpg" alt="SumoSpin Timeline" style="width:auto;">
                              </picture>
                          </div>                     
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <div class="col-lg-8 offset-2 col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-8">
                        <p>There are a lot of plans for Sumo Spin!  There's no set dates or hard goals right now but this represents the general direction we hope to take.  Utilizing feedback at each stage will help us improve the next, both by working with beta testers and by engaging with feedback from regular users.  If you think that sounds interesting, use the sign up form located above!  We need all kinds of players!</p>

                        <p>Moving from browser to mobile will still preserve our 1 device, 2 players mechanic but now from your preferred app store and mobile device.  During this period, we will be working with feedback from both Android and iOS users to get a game plan together for Kickstarting the PC launch.</p>

                        <p>The PC port will have new modes and features- not all of which are decided, atm.  We're really excited to develop a battle royale mode that can support up to 8 players and controller support.  We have other goals, too, like original music and extra game types.</p>

                        <p>Getting Sumo Spin to a console release would be awesome- the  processes for that are murky right now, so we're focusing our energy on developing Sumo Spin into its best self one step at a time.  But maybe someday! </p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
